(30653, 11372, 1789, 4, '決裂 (2010)', '加入新成員 2010 重新編曲\r\n(12/21重新上傳)', '2010-12-21 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 9, 'Face you,like face the stranger\r\nI''m looking your face\r\nbut you always keep the silence\r\n眼角餘光露出\r\n一絲冷漠\r\n為何妳的瞳孔\r\n充滿不安與燥動\r\n\r\n徹底丟棄曾經所有\r\n我還擁有什麼 \r\n回憶留下傷痛\r\n逃離醜陋的夢 \r\n\r\n無法跳脫\r\n憎恨寂寞\r\n崩潰失落\r\n噪音傷痛\r\n\r\n情感幻滅\r\n背叛承諾\r\n看著你那虛假的瞳\r\nFuckin leave me alone !\r\n\r\nI cross the lonly road,but I can''t forget your lips\r\nthe lonly road,and you will out of my life\r\n\r\nYour promise  like the shit\r\nThis is my nightmare\r\n \r\nFace you,like face the stranger\r\nI''m looking your face\r\nbut you always keep the silence\r\n眼角餘光露出\r\n一絲冷漠\r\n為何妳的沉默\r\n決裂妳我之間\r\n\r\n無法跳脫現實虛幻束縛\r\n憎恨將我淹沒\r\n崩潰失落徹底使我懦弱\r\n傷痛將我擊破\r\n\r\n情感幻滅使我眼神空洞\r\n背叛承諾將我思緒掏空\r\n看著妳那虛假的瞳\r\nFuckin leave me alone !\r\n\r\nI cross the lonly road,but I can''t forget your lips\r\nthe lonly road,and you will out of my life ', '', 229, '', 'SaKeens', 'SaKeens', '', '雜牌', '', 0, 1, 0, '2010-12-22 01:28:11', '2015-03-12 13:45:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
